{"tid":804124,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇絲打同我一樣，鍾意係床上面俾男人控制一切？","createTime":"2018-09-02T18:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T06:54:04.000Z","uid":82845,"like":4,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"23609ab61a66de3cb6b11253e298188b7d9b5dcb","tid":804124,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T18:56:25.000Z","msg":"近排我搵番ex扑野，佢係一個要係床上控制一切嘅男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如有一次佢要求我除晒衫自慰俾佢睇，我覺得好羞恥所以唔肯，跟住佢好大力打左我兩巴（係嘴邊有血絲嗰種）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再用命令嘅語氣迫我自慰。雖然我喺佢面前表現到好唔開心，但其實內心好享受。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一次，佢喺未沖涼嘅情況下要我幫佢含撚，我唔願意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後佢罰我跪喺地下兩個鐘，中途佢強行擘大我個口，再放條撚入嚟，最後口爆埋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然，都係同上一次一樣，同樣喺佢面前扮唔開心，但其實內心好享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以上就係我呢排同ex扑野時其中兩次最深刻嘅經歷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我鐘意喺床上俾男人控制，而佢正正係呢種人（亦係同我現任男友嘅最大分別）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我相信未來都會繼續搵佢爆房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果其他絲打都有呢種僻好嘅話，歡迎一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留低tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46162dc2dcf613c2eb7bc5495f244454ca17a4b3","tid":804124,"uid":120955,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T19:01:29.000Z","msg":"互射咗幾多次"},{"pid":"f2251c1638a36540178459675eb7470aca0f0e92","tid":804124,"uid":204331,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T19:04:30.000Z","msg":"含臭鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68579eaef5b6334e1624b67c12a107431d87fc73","tid":804124,"uid":60049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"